 ◥▎▎▏▏░░§b▜███▛§0░░▏▏▎▎◤
  ◥▎▎▏▏░◤  §b▀▀▀§0  ◥░▏▏▎▎◤
#- 
    Abjuration magic,
represented here by
a chest plate with
wings, is used to
protect and block.

    Abjuration can
come from multiple
sources such as
Alchemy, Beacons, and
Enchantments.
#- 
    Abjuration is
often sought out for
its protective
properties, making it
exceedingly popular
for armour.

    Enchantments
includes Protection of
all types, Feather
Falling, Mending,
Unbreaking, and even
Thorns.
#- 
    Alchemy sources
include Golden Apples
and Enchanted Golden
Apples, Fire
Resistance potions,
and Slow Falling
potions.

    Beacons also
provides some
abjuration with the
Resistance effect.
#- 
       Ｃｏｎｊｕｒａｔｉｏｎ

§f＿＿＿＿＿§0◢▙▖
