§f＿＿＿ §3▝▀▄▄▀▘
#- 
    Divination magic,
represented here by
an Eye of Ender,
provides information
that was previously
unknown.

    Examples include
Eyes of Ender guiding
users to strongholds
and Spectral Arrows
showing the location
of your target.
#- 
         Ｅｖｏｃａｔｉｏｎ

§f＿＿＿＿＿＿§4▞◤    ◣
§f＿＿＿＿＿§4◣▜▖◢◥
