#- 
    Illusion magic,
represented here by
a figure turning
invisible, is magic that
deceives the mind.

    Effects include
both invisibility and
blindness; users
include Wandering
Traders and the
rarely seen
Illusioner.
#- 
       Ｎｅｃｒｏｍａｎｃｙ

     ▄▀▀▀▀▀▀▄
    ▞§f＿＿＿＿＿＿＿§0▚
