§f▎§0       ▌▄▌§f＿§0▌▄▌
#- 
    Transmutation
magic, represented
here by a Iron Golem,
alters the properties
of creatures and
things.

    Examples of
transmutation are
Iron and Snow Golems,
Slimes, Magma Cubes,
Guardians and Elder
Guardians.
#- 
         Ａｌｃｈｅｍｙ

 §f＿＿ §6▄▖§f＿＿＿ §6▄▖
 §f＿＿§0▌§6▉▍§0▌ §6▄▖§0 ▌§6▉▌§0▌
