 §f＿＿§0▞ ▚ ▌ ▌ ▞ ▚
 §f＿§0▞§4██▌§0▛ ▜§2██▌§0▚
 §f＿§0▌§4██§0▞§1██▌§0▚§2█▉§0▌
 §f＿§0▚§4█▌§0▌§1█▉▉▌§0▌§2█▌§0▞
 §f＿＿§0▀▘▚§1██▌§0▞▝▀
 §f＿＿＿＿ §0▝▀▀
#- 
    Alchemy, pictured
here by a few potion
bottles, comes
directly as a result
of crafting.

    The most obvious
example of alchemy is
the creation of
potions through
brewing.
#- 
    Alchemy also
includes the creation
of other items such
as Eyes of Ender,
Golden Apples, Fire
Charges, and
Firework Rockets.

    This also includes
items used in brewing
such as Magma Cream
and Fermented Spider
Eyes.
#- 
    Users of alchemy
include Witches,
Clerics, and
interestingly also
includes Farmers.

    Farmers will offer
various Suspicious
Stews as well as
Golden Carrots and
Glistering Melon
Slices.
#- 
       Ｅｎｃｈａｎｔｍｅｎｔ

  §f＿＿ §b▟█▄§f＿ ＿§0⍑
   ∴§f＿＿§b▀▊▊▙▖§0▄◣
 §f＿＿＿＿＿§b▀██▌§0▌
