 §2▐▛▀▘◤§4◥▀▀◤
#- 
    Overturgy magic,
represented here by
a rose, is magic that
derives directly from
the Overworld
dimension.

    Overturgy
includes Iron Golems,
Snow Golems, Conduits,
and the Totem of
Undying.
#- 
      Ｎｅｔｈｅｒｍａｎｃｙ

