     ████████
     ████████
#- 
    Nethermancy magic,
represented here by
Nether portal, is
magic that derives
directly from the
Nether dimension.

    This includes
Withered Roses, the
Wither, Magma Cubes,
and Soul Sand.
#- 
       Ｅｎｄｅｒｍａｎｃｙ

